<p>How find most expensive department?  </p>  <p>I need to find the most expensive department (deptno) with use XPath 1.0. Structure of the my XML document next. </p>  <pre><code>    &lt;employee deptno="10" empno="7369" mgr="7902"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;SMITH&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;800.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="30" empno="7499" mgr="7698"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;ALLEN&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;1600.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="30" empno="7521" mgr="7698"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;WARD&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;1250.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="20" empno="7566" mgr="7839"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;JONES&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;2975.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="30" empno="7654" mgr="7698"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;MARTIN&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;1250.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="30" empno="7698" mgr="7839"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;BLAKE&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;2850.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="10" empno="7782" mgr="7839"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;CLARK&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;2450.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="20" empno="7788" mgr="7566"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;SCOTT&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;3000.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="10" empno="7839"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;KING&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;5000.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="30" empno="7844" mgr="7698"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;TURNER&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;1500.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="20" empno="7876" mgr="7788"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;ADAMS&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;1100.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="30" empno="7900" mgr="7698"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;JAMES&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;950.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="20" empno="7902" mgr="7566"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;FORD&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;3000.00&lt;/sal&gt;         &lt;comm&gt;0.0&lt;/comm&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt;     &lt;employee deptno="10" empno="7934" mgr="7782"&gt;         &lt;ename&gt;MILLER&lt;/ename&gt;         &lt;sal&gt;1300.00&lt;/sal&gt;     &lt;/employee&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Result must be department with number 20 because sum by 20 dept = 10075 > 9550 (dept 10) > 9400 (dept 30).</p>  <p><strong>Edit:</strong> New version XML document added</p>